282
00:30:47,070 --> 00:30:50,190
If our meeting was a mistake,

283
00:30:52,200 --> 00:30:57,990
now it's time for this mistake to end.

284
00:31:02,430 --> 00:31:04,980
I hope for the rest of our lives,

285
00:31:07,360 --> 00:31:09,760
