00:33:23,280 --> 00:33:25,660
Young Master, you're awake.

305
00:33:30,250 --> 00:33:32,340
Was Young Madam here?

306
00:33:32,340 --> 00:33:33,960
Young Madam?

307
00:33:33,960 --> 00:33:37,490
Isn't she living in Tingxiang Yard?

308
00:33:37,490 --> 00:33:41,830
This morning she went to the cemetery with Seventh Madame and the Fourth Miss.

309
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:50,790
