329
00:35:19,720 --> 00:35:23,050
- Get off me!
- Be careful!

330
00:35:24,170 --> 00:35:28,040
Get out of the way.

331
00:35:28,040 --> 00:35:29,540
Go back!

332
00:35:29,540 --> 00:35:31,950
Let me go!

333
00:35:31,950 --> 00:35:34,850
